          "difficulty": 3,
          "score": 3.1021232876712332
        },
        {
          "comment": "Professor Amegbor is very knowledgable and put a lot of work in to make sure the content in our class had a wide range of perspectives, which was appreciated. The class was mostly lectures which got a little bit boring but occasionally there would be group activities during class. He is a kind person though and wants to get to know his students",
