      "review_highlights": [
        {
          "comment": "One of the most practical and useful classes I took for my MHA degree. He gave real world examples of how the info/topics in the weekly readings and lectures applied to the different types of healthcare professions of students in the class. He explained how it all connects, making it relevant and interesting. Very interactive, takes attendance.",
          "class_name": "HPAMGP4848",
          "grade": "A",
          "date": "2019-07-11",
          "clarity": 5,
          "helpful": 5,
          "difficulty": 3,
          "score": 1.73
        },
        {
          "comment": "David Quirk personifies all you hope to find in a professional graduate program professor. His class delved into timely topics that other courses did not touch. His demeanor allows for difficult concepts to be understood and he's very receptive to questions. His professional career is so impressive, and is a real benefit to graduate students!",
          "class_name": "GP4848",
          "grade": "",
          "date": "2019-09-13",
          "clarity": 5,
          "helpful": 5,
          "difficulty": 3,
          "score": 1.72
        },
        {
          "comment": "David was a great professor. Learned a lot in his class - very lecture heavy. But he is super helpful if you have any questions. The class tends to go over but that is because he is really passionate about the topic on hand, which is a great thing. I wish there were more papers in this class because he gives really good feedback on them.",
          "class_name": "HPAM4848",
          "grade": "",
          "date": "2019-07-12",
          "clarity": 5,
          "helpful": 5,
          "difficulty": 3,
          "score": 1.695
        },
        {
          "comment": "Initially took this class to fill grade requirements, I was pleasantly surprised by the professor and the material. It was only a 7 week class so there is a lot of information to get through but he made it interesting. Besides schooling you on the content at hand, he offered up some great overall life advice.",
          "class_name": "HPAMGP4848",
          "grade": "A",
          "date": "2019-07-17",
          "clarity": 5,
          "helpful": 5,
          "difficulty": 3,
          "score": 1.55
        },
        {
